# Build

To build astral-box, run

	./configure
	make

For more configuration options, see

	./configure --help

# Test

To run all of the checks, run

	make check

To run the check for a specific <util>, run

	make check-<util>

# Install

To install astral-box, run

	make install

# Uninstall

To uninstall astral-box, run

	make uninstall
